OL,3,CEx-City footballer Benjamin Mendy
OL,4,Cgiven more time to clear tax debt
OL,6,FFormer defender Benjamin Mendy has
OL,7,Fbeen given more time to clear a debt
OL,8,Fsaid to be around #800,000.
OL,10,FThe High Court previously heard HM
OL,11,FRevenue and Customs (HMRC) is seeking
OL,12,Fa bankruptcy order against the
OL,13,Ffootballer over a six-figure bill.
OL,15,FMr Mendy has been given more time to
OL,16,Fsettle the debt after the court was
OL,17,Ftold a buyer was now in place for the
OL,18,Ffootballer's house near , .
