OL,3,CEx-City footballer Benjamin Mendy
OL,4,Cgiven more time to clear tax debt
OL,6,FThe short hearing before a specialist
OL,7,Finsolvency judge in London, was told
OL,8,Fthe property is now being sold for
OL,9,F#3.8 million having previously been
OL,10,Flisted for #5 million ` with the sale
OL,11,Fexpected to complete in eight weeks.
OL,13,FLouis Doyle KC, for Mr Mendy, said:
OL,14,F"He wants to get rid of this debt as
OL,15,Fquickly as he possibly can.
OL,17,F"If we get 10 weeks down the line and
OL,18,Fit is still not sold, I accept I might
OL,19,Fhave a very different fight on my
OL,20,Fhands."
