OL,3,CEx-City footballer Benjamin Mendy
OL,4,Cgiven more time to clear tax debt
OL,6,FThe court also heard Mr Mendy is
OL,7,Fbringing legal action against his
OL,8,Fformer club after Manchester City
OL,9,Fstopped paying him when he was charged
OL,10,Fwith rape in 2021. The footballer was
OL,11,Fsubsequently cleared of rape and
OL,12,Fattempted rape at Chester Crown Court.
OL,14,FMr Doyle said that Mr Mendy being made
OL,15,Fbankrupt could have a "potentially
OL,16,Fcatastrophic impact" on his claim
OL,17,Fwhich is due to go into mediation
OL,18,Flater this year.
