OL,3,CEx-City footballer Benjamin Mendy
OL,4,Cgiven more time to clear tax debt
OL,6,FAt the previous hearing in October, Mr
OL,7,FDoyle said Mr Mendy was prepared to
OL,8,Fpay #20,000 a month to HMRC from his
OL,9,Fsalary from his new employer, French
OL,10,Fclub Lorient.
OL,12,FHowever, the court was told these
OL,13,Fpayments had not been made, in part
OL,14,Fbecause the footballer had not
OL,15,Freceived a bonus he was expecting from
OL,16,Fthe new club.
