OL,6,FGranting a 12-week adjournment to
OL,7,Fallow for the sale of Mr Mendy's
OL,8,Fhouse, Judge Joseph Curl KC said:
OL,9,F"Although I am troubled by the failure
OL,10,Fto pay the #20,000 per month and that
OL,11,Fthis is now a fourth adjournment, I am
OL,12,Fpersuaded that I should give what Mr
OL,13,FDoyle described as 'the benefit of the
OL,14,Fdoubt'."
